<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="W" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Whoeer" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Whoe'er,</orth> any one that; whatever person: <bibl n="shak. son 133.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 133, 11</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.2.103" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 2, 103</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 4.1.4" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 1, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.4.37" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A V, 4, 37</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.3.12" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B IV, 3, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.2.107" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 2, 107</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.3.7" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 1.3.65" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 3, 65</bibl>. Unchanged in the accus.: <cit><quote>w. I woo, myself would be his wife,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 1.4.42" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 4, 42</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>w. you find attach,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 5.3.173" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. V, 3, 173</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>